---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import WhatsAppButton from '../components/WhatsAppButton.astro';
---

<Layout title="Nadi Astrology Procedure - How It Works">
  <Header />
  
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-800">
          Nadi Astrology Procedure
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 text-center mb-12 leading-relaxed">
          Understanding the step-by-step process of authentic Nadi Astrology reading
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 to-transparent border-l-4 border-primary p-6 rounded">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
                1
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-800">Thumb Impression</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  The process begins with taking your thumb impression (right thumb for males, left for females). This unique impression is scientifically proven to be distinct for every individual and serves as the key to finding your palm leaf.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 to-transparent border-l-4 border-primary p-6 rounded">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
                2
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-800">Palm Leaf Identification</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  Based on your thumb impression pattern, the Nadi reader searches through bundles of palm leaves to find the ones that match your specific impression category. This can take time as the leaves are carefully examined.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 to-transparent border-l-4 border-primary p-6 rounded">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
                3
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-800">Verification Process</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  The reader will verify your identity by reading general information from the leaf - your name, parents' names, spouse's name (if married), and other personal details. You confirm yes or no to each statement until your exact leaf is found.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 to-transparent border-l-4 border-primary p-6 rounded">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
                4
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-800">Reading the Predictions</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  Once your leaf is identified, the Nadi reader translates the ancient Tamil script and reveals your past, present, and future. This includes details about your life events, challenges, relationships, career, and spiritual path.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 to-transparent border-l-4 border-primary p-6 rounded">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="bg-primary text-white rounded-full w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl mr-4 flex-shrink-0">
                5
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-800">Remedial Solutions</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">
                  The reading concludes with specific remedial measures prescribed for overcoming obstacles and challenges in your life. These may include poojas, mantras, gemstones, or other spiritual practices tailored to your situation.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg p-8 mt-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-800">What to Bring</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>✓ Your birth details (if available, though not mandatory)</li>
            <li>✓ An open mind and respectful attitude</li>
            <li>✓ Questions you want answered about your life</li>
            <li>✓ Patience for the verification process</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center mt-12">
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-secondary transition-colors">
            Book Your Reading
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <Footer />
  <WhatsAppButton />
</Layout>
